n-logs/asm:asm:3.1/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T20-11-55-346242Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/asm:asm:3.1/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T20-19-53-807118Z.log`.\n\nNext steps:\n1. Start from the preserved branch and replace/remove the scaffold `AsmTest` with real ASM-specific coverage.\n2. Rework `ClassReaderTest` and `ClassWriterTest` so native execution actually reaches the two tracked call sites above, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=asm:asm:3.1`.\n3. Confirm `tests/src/asm/asm/3.1/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json` improves before opening a PR."}}
